name: The Annual Conference on Life Sciences and Engineering
content: The Annual Conference on Life Sciences and Engineering (ACLSE 2015) will be held in Osaka, Japan during August 25-27, 2015\. The aim objective is to provide a platform for researchers, engineers, academicians as well as industrial professionals from all over the world to present their research results and development activities in Life Sciences and Engineering. This conference provides opportunities for the delegates to exchange new ideas and application experiences face to face, to establish business or research relations and to find global partners for future collaboration.
